dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2019. [This is a 'point' feature class representing the location where the driveway meets the road right of way. It contains the House Number and Street Name (Address). The parcel number is also included for each address 'point'.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
